  keywords  = {*Evolution, Molecular,*Mutation,Alleles,Anti-Bacterial Agents/*pharmacology,Cefotaxime/*pharmacology,Dose-Response Relationship, Drug,Drug Resistance, Microbial/*genetics,Escherichia coli Proteins/genetics/metabolism,Escherichia coli/*drug effects/*genetics,Models, Genetic,PBP3,Pyrophosphatases/genetics/metabolism,TEM-1,epistasis,mutational pathways,mutator},
